│ valid JSON object. Put all other content outside of these    │
│ tags.                                                        │
│ 3. The "args" field MUST also be a valid JSON object. It is  │
│ NOT a string that represents a JSON object.                  │
│ 4. Only call ONE tool in each of your response. Do NOT call  │
│ multiple tools at the same time.                             │
